  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "At the most fundamental level, most of the challenges to RAG relate to data management and machine learning operations (MLOps) capabilities.",
    "Data management has been identified as a major challenge in IS research (Abbasi et al. 2016) in general.",
    "Since RAG-based systems require additional efforts to merge data from heterogeneous data sources, these challenges are compounded.",
    "Therefore, organizations need to develop additional capabilities to address this need.",
    "Modern concepts such as data mesh structures (Dehghani 2022; Blohm et al. 2024) can also be considered as a useful approach for developing RAG-based systems."
  ],
